{"tid":1749922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以唔好再po燒山啲嘢","createTime":"2019-11-24T07:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T08:39:58.000Z","uid":34515,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea227a814dccd54ec8920dc2f4b0cd80173f3b3d","tid":1749922,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係研究佢啲論點<br />\n佢燈又點唔燈又點<br />\n講嘢唔準咪由得佢囉<br />\n<br />\n重點係佢講乜都上熱門 仲要幾個熱門<br />\n搞到啲行動post冇晒<br />\n個個都 &lsquo;又燈&lsquo; &rsquo;收皮啦&lsquo; <br />\n搞到好冇討論價值<br />\n<br />\n雖然我認同得閒放鬆下係好<br />\n但真係好無謂<br />\n仲有好多po上嚟嘅<br />\n都係無限放大佢一句嘢<br />\n跟住又好多人推post<br />\n<br />\n某程度上我覺得佢有啲point係值得我哋思考<br />\n不過好似好多連登仔都唔係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e736b183fb1ae91848082265f3178bf9bc3bd84","tid":1749922,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"呢條怨婦幾時先收皮"},{"pid":"36b12d14aa4ea1e490b628476d9ac8553dfe9dc4","tid":1749922,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n香港人想進行就要深入認真討論政治，諷刺野間中up下就夠"},{"pid":"b5e534d3f40a3ea44f5dfe72e87b8ad78649d7e8","tid":1749922,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"燒山份人慘在乜野都要發表意見<br />\nD野唔撚識都要學人評論<br />\n最慘係無口齒，明明之前話收山唔再評時事又姣婆守唔到寡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6e9a131acb2ca9037e9ae8def3e1de73e55f99","tid":1749922,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e736b183fb1ae91848082265f3178bf9bc3bd84","tid":1749922,"uid":117237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"呢條怨婦幾時先收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:56:09.000Z","msg":"你講我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4db6048bd31f7b77df532ca1fc29675eebe981","tid":1749922,"uid":23